divs: Sighting DetailsThese people started freaking out down the street by the woods. I didnt knowwhat it was but upon closer inspection there were several forms running aroundthem. i was really scared but i managed to take a picture. it came out blank.the flash from the camera might have frightened them, because they got into thislittle pod thing and flew off in the blink of an eye. the people were OK, butone of them said he couldnt breath for about 20 seconds.
Summary: Saw aliens run at unbelievable speeds
